# ── Public, tracked (the plugin ships these) ────────────────────────────
#   .claude-plugin/      plugin manifest + marketplace catalog
#   skills/              one folder per slash command (modern layout)
#   agents/              the priors-steward subagent
#   hooks/               lifecycle hooks for Claude Code
#   .mcp.json            MCP server config
#   .cursor/rules/       Cursor-side operating rule
#   .cursor/mcp.json     Cursor MCP server config
#
# ── Personal / dev-only (gitignored — never part of the plugin) ─────────
